#Bundesliga winner of the week: @HerthaBSC

A big win for @HerthaBSC against @VfB. @HerthaBSC now with big chances to avoid relegation.

@FCBayern is champion again!

@RBLeipzig, @bayer04fussball, @scfreiburg, @fcunion, and @fckoeln within just six points. https://t.co/ZpGy21ISIM

WEEKEND ROUND-UP…
#BUNDESLIGA: Bayern beat Dortmund. Bayern won the league. Tale as old as time.

@RBLeipzig conceded two late goals to lose 2-1 at home to Union Berlin, they slip to 4th with a 4-1 win for @bayer04_en at Greuter Fürth meaning they leapfrog Leipzig back into 3rd.
